Detailed Description

template<class TESTEDCLASS>
class CurlAccountConfirmMailTest< TESTEDCLASS >

A test class for CurlAccountConfirmMail

We test the setName and getName functions with a default value and a setted name.

We must use a virtual account to test this curl-based class. We first use the virtual account. Its mail shouldn't confirmed and we test it.

We then confirm the mail address and test the connection if the error changed.
